Distribution . Only recorded from two areas: near Victoria, Cameroon ( type locality) and along Namibia , in depths from 400 to 710 m (
Doflein & Balss 1913
;
Macpherson 1983
). Our records extend the geographical distribution northwards to Mauritania and also increase its bathymetrical range from 710 to 1530 m deep.
